{"tid":2241013,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"橋水創辦人達里奧：時機在中國一方　人民幣國際化改寫世界秩序","createTime":"2020-10-13T05:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T12:04:17.000Z","uid":1086,"like":7,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"dd11423795e9d7533e86ed762c2ea4adf9d8f147","tid":2241013,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2775000/2775383/20201013_dalio_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2775000%2F2775383%2F20201013_dalio_1024.jpg&h=85d4d71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全球最大對沖基金橋水（Bridgewater），其創辦人達里奧（Ray Dalio）近期屢提及美國經濟、美元秩序或面臨結構危機，達利奧美國時間周一出席論壇時指出，中國一系列環節中都較美國更有優勢，「時機站在中國一方，而非美國」，並形容人民幣國際化將改寫美元秩序。<br />\n<br />\n達里奧指，新冠肺炎疫情下，中國經濟較美國更快反彈，中國企業新股IPO火熱，吸引大量資金買入，而且中國利率較美國高，反映中國處於更佳位置「毋須印鈔」。他續稱：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>美國新任政府面對的困難是，命運愈來愈站在中國，而且中國發展很可能愈來愈好。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n達里奧：資本主義需重新設計 「美國如75年帝國 勢力正減弱」<br />\n<br />\n達里奧於7月時曾帖文稱，中美緊張局勢可能由經濟角力演變成武力衝突，引用二次大戰歷史為鑑，形容經濟戰往往是武裝大戰前哨，又指中美很可能捲入資本戰。<br />\n<br />\n他最新在論壇抱相同看法，他稱「大家將看到人民幣國際化，這在以往無意的發展方向，因為這將影響美國的世界秩序。」<br />\n<br />\n今年橋水旗下基金表現不彰，旗艦基金Pure Alpha II 在8月下跌18.6%，橋水的資產管理規模最新約1480億美元，較年初減少120億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2775383/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2775383%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=0c9b41db\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2775383/</a><br />\n<br />\nRead More:<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2755000/2756489/20200918_Dalio_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2755000%2F2756489%2F20200918_Dalio_1024.jpg&h=b9733da2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n達利奧：資本主義需重新設計 「美國如75年帝國 勢力正減弱」<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2756489/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2756489%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbdVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=6313dfbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2756489/</a>"},{"pid":"cf0742c15c83f937c3fcb2090d0c16e243d37ad5","tid":2241013,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"ray dalio 好撐支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882164d874d8c3a8549e5dfe306659c084e28828","tid":2241013,"uid":142574,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"今年橋水旗下基金表現不彰，旗艦基金Pure Alpha II 在8月下跌18.6%，橋水的資產管理規模最新約1480億美元，較年初減少120億美元<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380efd85c0c2c3215511a272821dfeac5b0d6bf9","tid":2241013,"uid":92188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"白皮支心"},{"pid":"7e991aeaa01b45d300cc87c346de2cc71390db4c","tid":2241013,"uid":36845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"連自己果範都未做好，憑咩信你其他方面既言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb005d35a98e88236cd5f7b5fffd4222048b024","tid":2241013,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"大戶放風嚟講..."},{"pid":"12fe55e87fd9e1996f2a74fe3d259e0c55a983ee","tid":2241013,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"依家D廢老呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80f8633691071a084bb74df6da57b04fb9c0743","tid":2241013,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/e5f0